OL,3,CScientists observe Mounjaro slashing
OL,4,Cfood cravings by suppressing brain
OL,5,Csignals
OL,7,FScientists have observed that Mounjaro
OL,8,Freduces food cravings by suppressing
OL,9,Fbrain signals linked to eating
OL,10,Fcontrol, in a first-of-its-kind study.
OL,12,FResearchers in the US placed
OL,13,Felectrodes in the brain of a patient
OL,14,Fon the drug to study its impact on the
OL,15,Fregion associated with pleasure,
OL,16,Fmotivation and reward.
