OL,3,CScientists observe Mounjaro slashing
OL,4,Cfood cravings by suppressing brain
OL,5,Csignals
OL,7,FMounjaro, also known as tirzepatide,
OL,8,Fis a GLP-1 agonist, a type of
OL,9,Fmedication which mimics the hormone
OL,10,Fglucagon-like peptide-1 to help manage
OL,11,Fblood sugar levels and promote weight
OL,12,Floss.
OL,14,FThe study included three severely
OL,15,Fobese patients who struggled to
OL,16,Fcontrol their eating habits.
OL,18,FResearchers analysed the brain
OL,19,Factivity, recorded directly with
OL,20,Felectrodes implanted in the brain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
