OL,3,CScientists observe Mounjaro slashing
OL,4,Cfood cravings by suppressing brain
OL,5,Csignals
OL,7,FResearchers also recorded a decline in
OL,8,Fdelta-theta brain activity in the
OL,9,Fpatient on Mounjaro.
OL,11,FHowever, these brain signals and food
OL,12,Fcravings returned a few months later.
OL,14,FThe findings, published in the journal
OL,15,FNature Medicine, suggest the drug may
OL,16,Ftackle food cravings by affecting the
OL,17,Fbrain signal biomarkers associated
OL,18,Fwith eating control.
