OL,3,CScientists observe Mounjaro slashing
OL,4,Cfood cravings by suppressing brain
OL,5,Csignals
OL,7,FDr Simon Cork, a senior lecturer in
OL,8,Fphysiology at Anglia Ruskin
OL,9,FUniversity, said the study "is
OL,10,Fmethodologically very interesting".
OL,12,FBut he warned that it was only
OL,13,Fobserved in a single patient, so more
OL,14,Fstudy was needed.
OL,16,F"This study specifically looked at a
OL,17,Fmarker of brain activity associated
OL,18,Fwith periods of 'binge eating' in
OL,19,Fpatients with obesity associated with
OL,20,Ffood preoccupation," he said.
