OL,3,CScientists observe Mounjaro slashing
OL,4,Cfood cravings by suppressing brain
OL,5,Csignals
OL,7,F"This is important because this is a
OL,8,Fspecific (and rare) condition
OL,9,Fassociated with obesity.
OL,11,F"We know from animal studies that
OL,12,Fdirectly record from neurons in this
OL,13,Fregion of the brain that GLP-1 does
OL,14,Fsuppress activity of this region of
OL,15,Fthe brain, and this suppression is
OL,16,Flikely associated with the reduction
OL,17,Fin 'food noise' that patients with
OL,18,Fobesity often report.
