OL,12,F"It is also likely to be one of the
OL,13,Freasons why this drug class is seeing
OL,14,Fincreased interest in combating
OL,15,Faddictive conditions, such as alcohol
OL,16,Fand drug abuse.
OL,18,FMounjaro ` dubbed the King Kong of
OL,19,Fweight-loss injections ` is approved
OL,20,Ffor use on the NHS to treat type 2
OL,21,Fdiabetes and manage weight.
