OL,7,FThe health service has started its
OL,8,Froll-out of the drug for obesity, but
OL,9,Fthere are tight restrictions on which
OL,10,Fpatients are eligible.
OL,12,FOver three years, the NHS expects to
OL,13,Fgive the jabs to 240,000 people.
